title: Conor Oberst - Outer South (2009) [VIPER666]
description:
Outer South is the fifth solo album by Conor Oberst and the first credited to Conor Oberst and the Mystic Valley Band. It is Oberst's first solo album to include songs written and sung by his bandmates. Nik Freitas, Taylor Hollingsworth and Jason Boesel each contributed two songs apiece, and bassist Macey Taylor sings a song written for him by Conor. The album will be released on May 5, 2009 on Merge Records.
